---
// Testimonials Component - Fisiodermy
---

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="testimonials-bg"></div>
  
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonials-header animate-on-scroll">
      <p class="section-label centered">Testimonios</p>
      <h2 class="testimonials-title">
        Lo que dicen <em>nuestras pacientes</em>
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="testimonials-slider animate-on-scroll delay-2">
      <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
      
      <p class="testimonial-text">
        Excelente atención y resultados increíbles. El tratamiento post operatorio fue 
        fundamental para mi recuperación. Me sentí acompañada en todo el proceso y los 
        resultados superaron mis expectativas.
      </p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="testimonial-avatar">MC</div>
        <div class="testimonial-info">
          <h4>María Cristina</h4>
          <p>Paciente de Post Operatorio</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-stars">
        {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
          </svg>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Decorative Elements -->
  <div class="testimonials-decor testimonials-decor-1"></div>
  <div class="testimonials-decor testimonials-decor-2"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    background: var(--black);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonials-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 50%, rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.06) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 50%, rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.06) 0%, transparent 40%);
  }

  .testimonials-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .testimonials-title {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .testimonials-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .testimonials-slider {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 120px;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.2;
    line-height: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonial-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 30px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 25px;
  }

  .testimonial-avatar {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    background: var(--gold);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .testimonial-info h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .testimonial-info p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .testimonial-stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .testimonial-stars svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    fill: var(--gold);
  }

  /* Decorative Elements */
  .testimonials-decor {
    position: absolute;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.15);
  }

  .testimonials-decor-1 {
    top: 15%;
    left: 8%;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .testimonials-decor-2 {
    bottom: 15%;
    right: 8%;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-text {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .testimonial-quote {
      font-size: 80px;
    }

    .testimonials-decor {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
